    <h2>Objective:</h2>
    <p>The objective of Tarot is to score points by taking specific cards in tricks and fulfilling contracts.</p>

    <h2>Players:</h2>
    <p>Tarot is typically played by 3 to 5 players.</p>

    <h2>Setup:</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>A standard deck of 78 Tarot cards is used.</li>
        <li>The deck consists of 4 suits: Cups, Coins, Swords, and Batons, each numbered from 1 to 10, and 21 Trump cards.</li>
        <li>Trump cards have special abilities and are ranked higher than the numbered cards.</li>
    </ol>

